reviewText: At time of writing the item has not arrived and its taking a long time considering I ordered it on 26 October.

If you love David Hamilton's films you will like this collection. These DVDS unfortunately suffer from low picture quality, but they are still viewable enough to enjoy. David Hamilton definitely knows how to capture the sweetness of innocence, and still infuse it with blooming sensuality. This particular collection is also All Region, NTSC Format, despite the description in the catergory. (But be sure to check with the sellers selling it just to be sure).
